    "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/decision/dr-morrison-cou1-cpb-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped to not-assessed at MRL 2 with documented justification. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predictions of pressure rise, velocity field, wall shear stress, hemolysis index, and impeller torque are within pre-specified acceptance thresholds. The RH < 1 criterion is satisfied at all 5 COU operating points. Although aleatory uncertainty from blood property variability and experimental repeatability is discussed qualitatively in the validation report, the overall evidence body is sufficient to support the submission decision for this Class II device at MRL 2.",
    "decidedAt": "2026-04-19T00:00:00Z"
  },
